item.title: Analytics Commons
item.description: Analytics Commons Talk This talk looked at few tools that our department relies heavily on. This talk was part of our IS department’s commons session to give employees the chance to share their skills with examples to set and follow. Top 5 tools Analytics uses Introduction We are hoping to give an insight into 5 tools that we rely heavily to make our life easy in Analytics department. In this document we cover below 5 tools
